<p>Dear <%= @booking.guest_name %>,</p>

<p>Your hotel reservation for <%= WEDDING[:couple_names_possessive] %> wedding has been confirmed! Here are your booking details:</p>

<div class="event-card">
  <table class="rsvp-table">
    <tr>
      <td>Confirmation #</td>
      <td><strong><%= @booking.confirmation_number %></strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Check-in</td>
      <td><strong><%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %></strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Check-out</td>
      <td><strong><%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %></strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Rooms</td>
      <td><strong><%= @booking.rooms %></strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Nights</td>
      <td><strong><%= @booking.nights %></strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Total Paid</td>
      <td><strong><%= @booking.amount_display %></strong></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <% if @booking.notes.present? %>
    <p class="meal-info">Notes: <%= @booking.notes %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<p>If you have any questions about your reservation, please reach out to us directly.</p>

<p>We can't wait to see you there!</p>

<p><%= WEDDING[:couple_names] %></p>
